  <brief_title>An Efficiency/Safety Study of Surgical Tissue Glue to Treat Inguinal Hernias</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cyanoacrylate Fixation for Laparoscopic Repair of Inguinal Hernias: a Prospective, Multicenter Registry</official_title>
  <sponsors>
