  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, multicenter, observational registry to collect data of laparoscopic inguinal
      hernia repair using surgical tissue glue fixation. The objective is to determine the
      prevalence of chronic pain at 1 year.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
